oseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-aAV","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26784,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/09\/05\/non-muslim-relative-dies\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: If a non-Muslim relative passes away","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: I said to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cYour uncle, the misguided old man, has died.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGo bury your father and do nothing until you come back to me.\u201d I buried him and I came back to him. The Prophet ordered me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/12\/22\/janazah-stand-funeral-respect\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Janazah: Stand up for funerals respectfully","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amir ibn Rabi'ah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you see a funeral procession, stand up for it until it passes or the deceased is placed in the grave.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1245, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 958 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26698,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/07\/03\/janazah-stand-or-sit\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Janazah: Better to stand for funerals, permissible to sit","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: We saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, stand for funerals and so we stood up. The Prophet would sit and so we sat. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 962 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cThe preferred opinion of Al-Mutawalli among our scholars is that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24280,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/funeral-good-witness\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Muslims whose good is witnessed enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever four persons testify to the goodness of a Muslim, he will enter Paradise.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd three?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven three.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd two?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven two.\u201d Thereafter, we did not ask\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40019,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/12\/jannah-lost-beloved\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Paradise for patience with lost loved ones","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is not satisfied for His believing servant to be rewarded with anything but Paradise if his loved ones on earth pass away, he remains patient, hopes for reward, and says what he has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26692,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/07\/03\/do-not-curse-the-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":40729,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Death: Do not curse the dead, hurt the living","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not abuse the dead and thus harm the living.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1982 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Imam al-San'ani commented, \"The prohibition of insulting the dead is general, including unbelievers or others.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40729","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyha